body:
I used this to install:

```
export TF_BINARY_URL=https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/linux/gpu/tensorflow-0.11.0rc0-cp35-cp35m-linux_x86_64.whl
sudo pip3 install --upgrade $TF_BINARY_URL
```

from [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/g3doc/get_started/os_setup.md). I'm assuming this is what will be updated?
